Click for Atc-exec-binary-strict-pure-rules in the Full Manual

Rules for executing strict pure binary operations.

The goal of these rules is to rewrite (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y) to (op-type1-type2 x y) when x has type type1, and y has type type2. We could have a rule for each combination of op, type1, and type2, but that would lead to 1,600 rules being applicable to (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y). So we stage the rewriting as follows:

  • First, we rewrite (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y) to a call (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op x y), under the hypothesis that op is a specific operator, where exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op is one of 16 functions, one per binary strict operator.
  • Next, we rewrite (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op x y) to a call (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op-and-type1 x y), under the hypothesis that x has type type1, where exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op-and-type1 is one of 10 functions, one per supported integer type.
  • Finally, we rewrite (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-op-and-type1 x y) to the call (op-type1-type2 x y), under the hypothesis the y has type type2, for each of the 10 supported integer types.

Note that the intermediate functions used here do not need guard verification.

Definitions and Theorems

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-mul x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-mul

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-mul
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-mul)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar
       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-mul (schar-fix x) y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-when-schar

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-when-schar
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (scharp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar x y))))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar-when-schar

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar-when-schar
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom y)
     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (scharp y)
   (mul-schar-schar-okp x y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar x y)
         (mul-schar-schar x y))))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-schar-when-uchar

                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary

   (mul-slong-sllong-okp x y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-mul-and-slong x y)
         (mul-slong-sllong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-div

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-div (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-div x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-div

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-div
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-div)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-div x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-rem

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-rem (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-rem x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-rem

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-rem
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-rem)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-rem x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-add x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-add

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-add
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-add)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add x y))))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add-when-sllong

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add-when-sllong
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (sllongp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-add-and-sllong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-sub x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-sub

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-sub
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-sub)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub x y))))

           (exec-sub (uint-fix x) y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-when-uint

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-when-uint
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (uintp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-and-uint x y))))

                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (uintp y)
   (sub-sllong-uint-okp x y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-and-sllong x y)
         (sub-sllong-uint x y))))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-and-sllong-when-slong

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-sub-and-sllong-when-slong
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom y)
     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (slongp y)
   (sub-sllong-slong-okp x y))

         (sub-sllong-slong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-shl x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-shl

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-shl
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-shl)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-and-schar

       (x y)

           (exec-shl (schar-fix x) y)))

       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-shl (sshort-fix x) y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-when-sshort

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-when-sshort
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (sshortp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-and-sshort x y))))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-and-sshort-when-schar

                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (scharp y)
   (shl-sshort-schar-okp x y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shl-and-sshort x y)
         (shl-sshort-schar x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-shr x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-shr

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-shr
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-shr)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr x y))))

     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (sshortp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr-and-sshort x y))))

     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (ullongp y)
   (shr-sllong-ullong-okp x y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-shr-and-sllong x y)
         (shr-sllong-ullong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-lt

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-lt (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-lt x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-lt

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-lt
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-lt)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-lt x y))))

 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-lt-and-ullong-when-ullong
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom y)
     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (ullongp y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-lt-and-ullong x y)
         (lt-ullong-ullong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-gt

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-gt (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-gt x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-gt

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-gt
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-gt)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-gt x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-gt-and-schar

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-gt-and-schar
       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-gt (schar-fix x) y)))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-le x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-le

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-le
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-le)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le x y))))

 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-and-sllong-when-sshort
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom y)
     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (sshortp y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-and-sllong x y)
         (le-sllong-sshort x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-and-ullong

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-and-ullong
       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-le (ullong-fix x) y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-when-ullong

(defthm
 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-when-ullong
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom x)
     (not (member-eq x
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (ullongp x))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le x y)
         (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-le-and-ullong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ge

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ge (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-ge x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-ge

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-ge
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-ge)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ge x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ge-and-schar

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ge-and-schar
       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-ge (schar-fix x) y)))

         (ge-ullong-sshort x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-eq

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-eq (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-eq x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-eq

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-eq
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-eq)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-eq x y))))

       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-ne x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-ne

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-ne
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-ne)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-ne x y))))

           (exec-bitand x y)))

 exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitand-and-sint-when-ullong
 (implies
  (and
   (syntaxp
    (or
     (atom y)
     (not (member-eq y
                     '(exec-ident exec-const
                                  exec-iconst exec-arrsub exec-unary
                                  exec-cast exec-binary-strict-pure
                                  exec-test exec-expr-pure)))))
   (ullongp y))
  (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitand-and-sint x y)
         (bitand-sint-ullong x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitand-and-uint

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitand-and-uint
       (x y)
       (b* ((y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-bitand (uint-fix x) y)))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitxor

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitxor (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-bitxor x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-bitxor

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-bitxor
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-bitxor)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitxor x y))))

         (bitxor-ullong-sshort x y))))

Function: exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitior

(defun exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitior (x y)
       (b* ((x (value-result-fix x))
            (y (value-result-fix y))
            ((when (errorp x)) x)
            ((when (errorp y)) y))
           (exec-bitior x y)))

Theorem: exec-binary-strict-pure-when-bitior

(defthm exec-binary-strict-pure-when-bitior
        (implies (and (equal op (binop-bitior)))
                 (equal (exec-binary-strict-pure op x y)
                        (exec-binary-strict-pure-of-bitior x y))))
